Class Board

java.lang.Object
  Board
All Implemented Interfaces:
Sudoku
public class Board
extends Object
implements Sudoku

Board class models the 9 by 9 rectangular array of squares. Each square can be blank or have an integer value from 1 to 9. Each square also has a list of possible values that can be used for that square's value.
